The paper discusses privacy and confidentiality challenges in the context of distributed ledger technology, which is a common topic in the computer security (cs.CR) and distributed computing (cs.DC) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the design of enterprise systems, which is relevant to the database (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), and cyber security (cs.CY) sub-categories.
